# 1. Create the timer objective if it doesn't exist
scoreboard objectives add ghast_timer dummy

# 2. Add 1 to the timer
scoreboard players add global ghast_timer 1

# 3. Every 400 ticks (20 seconds), try to spawn a Ghast
execute if score global ghast_timer matches 400.. run function adventure:spawn_ghast

# 4. Reset the timer if it hit the limit
execute if score global ghast_timer matches 400.. run scoreboard players set global ghast_timer 0